          </div>

          <div class="product-highlights">
            <div class="highlight-item">
              <h4>Accurate Alignment</h4>
              <p>Designed to support bearing positioning with stable structural precision.</p>
            </div>
            <div class="highlight-item">
              <h4>Strong Bracket Support</h4>
