        <h2>Product Features</h2>
        <ul class="feature-list">
          <li>Precision CNC-milled for stable dimensional consistency</li>
          <li>Designed for bearing support and accurate assembly alignment</li>
          <li>Suitable for automation equipment and industrial machinery systems</li>
